It's an API (an interface) to allow a software app to use the phones software and connectivity.

Without installing an app, it does nothing. 

It's the underlying interface that would allow a track and trace app to access Bluetooth and WiFi.

It's fine. This is how computers work https://t.co/72NNNfgIc0
